{"id": 2823, "genre": 1001, "title": "和对象（or 未来的对象）吵架，哪些话你觉得不该说？", "description": "那些火上浇油的、会让争吵升级的话都有哪些？", "record_count": 4703, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190304171803UK0DvzFrJBMdEOSs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-18T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 333824, "content": "你走开，你滚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602030}, {"id": 333825, "content": "算了。说了你也不会懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379590}, {"id": 333826, "content": "不要說你看看人家老婆那麼好，你咋就這麼矯情呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588848}, {"id": 333828, "content": "谈婚论嫁太远，能不说就不说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1547567}, {"id": 333829, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612910}, {"id": 334086, "content": "真不想跟你说了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613783}, {"id": 334855, "content": "随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615519}, {"id": 334859, "content": "说点啥呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601824}, {"id": 336907, "content": "小可爱，不要生气了呗！我知道错了生气伤身啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1624750}, {"id": 333837, "content": "明哲：你真的让我太失望了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612925}, {"id": 333838, "content": "括号内容真的是很关爱单身狗了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1255421}, {"id": 333839, "content": "戳穿队友有所伪装的事情，让双方更尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611702}, {"id": 333840, "content": "所有能够伤害到对方的气话，对于他的父母，他的朋友的抱怨及谩骂，还有拿他跟别人对比，提他的前女友等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612939}, {"id": 338448, "content": "就这样