99, "content": "“你的想法、做法、看法、行为、观点。。。等等等～真幼稚！”\n我qnmgb，最幼稚的是TM爱上你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613101}, {"id": 333644, "content": "能说话还算好吧。什么都不说，要么一直哭，要么瞪着你那种才可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 333645, "content": "拿前任和备胎来做和你做比较", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 333647, "content": "说什么都 哦 嗯 ", "image": "img/option/option/20190318112528UsL9Q78pmZ3bH4kf.jpg", "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612103}]}